- User authentication and role based access control
- Course registration with constraint enforcement (max 21 credits, max 3 failures per course)
- Three component marking system (first attestation, second attestation, final exam)
- Student transcript generation and GPA calculation
- Attendance tracking system

Research Management
- Research paper publication and management
- H-index calculation from paper citations
- Research project participation with role validation
- Journal subscriptions with automatic notifications
- Multiple citation formats (PlainText and BibTeX)
- Paper sorting by date, citations, or page length

Academic Administration
- Course assignment to teachers
- Student registration approval workflow
- Statistical reporting on academic performance
- News system with automatic research topic pinning
- News comments and discussion

Technical Support
- User submitted technical request workflow
- Request status tracking (VIEWED, ACCEPTED, REJECTED, DONE)
